summary: Adds a New Bow to the game for archers
descriptionHtml:
Adds a new bow to the game for archers, Luna\'s Favor, the bow is located North-West of Riverwood WELL hidden underwater in some rocks. The bow is a modify nightingal bow and doesn\'t need to be recharged. meant for users who just use the bow. The chest also has 1000 daedric arrows

Heres the Cheat Video for all ya cheaters out there
http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=n_01oV0R8nE&feature=youtu.be
